    <description>Heavy Gear Blitz! is the latest (2006) Heavy Gear miniatures game from Dream Pod 9. A much more streamlined version of the original tactical game but in a very new design.  Still holding true to the Silhouette game system old players should find the game very familiar and new players should find it fast and easy to learn.  Its eliminates the hex based maps and uses a to-scale terrain system familiar to most miniature games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The rulebook contains an introduction to the world of Terra Nova, the revised and streamlined rules, basic field guides for the forces on Terra Nova, a random scenario generator, 28 data cards covering all the standard vehicles in the field guides, as well as an assortment of counters for tracking the battle status of your army.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
